dct_title_s: Alaska and the routes of the Canadian Pacific Railway Company's British Columbia coast steamers
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Informational text under headings "Canadian Pacific Railway British Columbia steamship service," and "Connecting routes with Canadian Pacific British Columbia coast steamship service."
Canadian Pacific railways shown in red, others in black.
Shows railways (including proposed), waterways, coastal low water, glaciers, islands, cities, province boundaries, .
